pageContext.claim: “To the great and brave men and women of ICE, do not worry or lose your spirit. You are doing a fantastic job of keeping us safe by eradicating the worst criminal elements. So brave! The radical left Dems want you out. Next it will be all police. Zero chance, It will never happen!”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence that the calls by some Democrats to replace the Immigration enforcement agency would be followed by eliminating "all police."
